            <description><![CDATA[
							<h2>New Features</h2>
							<ul>
							    <li>Adds a basic icon search</li>
							    <li>Adds a view option to show icon names in the grid view</li>
							</ul>
							<h2>Fixes and Improvements</h2>
							<ul>
							    <li>Moves the settings for the low-resolution emulation to the Advanced tab in the Settings window</li>
							    <li>Updates the button for toggling low-resolution emulation</li>
							    <li>Author information for a selected collection is now displayed as a subtitle in the title bar</li>
							    <li>Fixes an issue where <em>Quick</em><strong>Drop</strong> could not set or remove the icon of files and folders</li>
							</ul>
							]]></description>
